1. ADJ You use wretched to describe someone or something that you dislike or feel angry with. 讨厌的 [非正式] [ADJ n] 

例： Wretched woman, he thought, why the hell can't she wait? 讨厌的女人，他想，她怎么就不能等等呢？ 

2. ADJ Someone who feels wretched feels very unhappy. 极不愉快的 [正式] 

例： I feel really confused and wretched. 我真的感到迷惑和难过。

